---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>👋 Welcome to databased.business</h1>

      <p><strong>Data is everywhere.</strong> But understanding it? That's where most people feel left behind.</p>

      <p>
        At <em>databased.business</em>, we’re here to change that.
        This space is designed by educators, analysts, and data enthusiasts who believe:
        <strong>data should be clear, open, and usable by everyone.</strong>
      </p>

      <hr />

      <h2>✨ What We're About</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Clarity over complexity</strong> – No jargon walls. Just clean, human explanations.</li>
        <li><strong>Empowerment through tools</strong> – We build interfaces that speak your language, not code.</li>
        <li><strong>Trust in transparency</strong> – You’ll always know where the numbers come from and what they mean.</li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <h2>🛠️ What We’re Building</h2>
      <p>We're working on tools and content to help you:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>🔍 Explore patterns without being a data scientist</li>
        <li>📈 Make decisions with confidence, not confusion</li>
        <li>📚 Learn as you go – no prior knowledge required</li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <h2>🚀 Join the Journey</h2>
      <p>
        This is just the beginning. Whether you’re data-curious or data-overwhelmed,
        you’re in the right place.
      </p>
      <p>
        Follow along, ask questions, challenge ideas – let's make data make sense, together.
      </p>

      <p>
        💬 Want to chat or collaborate? <strong>Reach out.</strong> We’re always happy to hear from fellow explorers.
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
